<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Business Major Career Paths</title>
    <style>
        /* Modern CSS Reset & Variables */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Quicksand', 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
        }

        :root {
            --navy-deep: #1e293b;       /* Crisp, professional dark navy */
            --navy-light: #334155;      /* Slate navy accent */
            --pink-soft: #fbcfe8;       /* Lovely light pastel pink background accents */
            --pink-accent: #f472b6;     /* Cute bubblegum pink for borders and highlights */
            --pink-deep: #db2777;       /* Dark pink for readable text on light backgrounds */
            --bg-creme: #f8fafc;        /* Clean off-white canvas */
            --card-bg: #ffffff;
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--bg-creme);
            color: var(--navy-deep);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* Actual Website Navigation Bar */
        nav {
            background-color: var(--navy-deep);
            padding: 10px 20px;
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.15);
            border-bottom: 3px solid var(--pink-accent);
        }

        .nav-container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            height: 60px;
        }

        .logo {
            color: white;
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }

        .logo span {
            color: var(--pink-accent);
        }

        /* Navigation Tabs Menu */
        .tab-menu {
            display: flex;
            gap: 8px;
            height: 100%;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .tab-label {
            padding: 10px 18px;
            color: #cbd5e1;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            border-radius: 20px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            user-select: none;
        }

        .tab-label:hover {
            color: var(--pink-accent);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        }

        /* Hide the state tracking radio buttons */
        .tab-input {
            display: none;
        }

        /* Interactive Tab Custom Selection Logic */
        #tab1:checked ~ nav .label1,
        #tab2:checked ~ nav .label2,
        #tab3:checked ~ nav .label3,
        #tab4:checked ~ nav .label4,
        #tab5:checked ~ nav .label5 {
            background: var(--pink-accent);
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(244, 114, 182, 0.4);
        }

        #tab1:checked ~ .container #content1,
        #tab2:checked ~ .container #content2,
        #tab3:checked ~ .container #content3,
        #tab4:checked ~ .container #content4,
        #tab5:checked ~ .container #content5 {
            display: block;
        }

        /* Header Hero Banner */
        header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy-deep), var(--navy-light));
            color: white;
            padding: 50px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        /* Cute decorative line under header */
        header::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 4px;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--pink-soft), var(--pink-accent));
        }

        header h1 {
            font-size: 2.6rem;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #ffffff;
        }

        header h1 span {
            color: var(--pink-accent);
        }

        header p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            color: #94a3b8;
        }

        /* Central Content Frame */
        .container {
            max-width: 1100px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            min-height: 450px;
        }

        .tab-panel {
            display: none;
            animation: popIn 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275) forwards;
        }

        /* High Contrast Rounded Cards */
        .content-card {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 24px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.05);
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }

        .content-card h2 {
            color: var(--navy-deep);
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            border-bottom: 3px solid var(--pink-soft);
            padding-bottom: 6px;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .content-card > p {
            color: var(--navy-light);
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            margin-top: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        /* Career Cards Showcases */
        .job-showcase {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 25px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .job-box {
            background: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            border-top: 4px solid var(--pink-accent);
            padding: 22px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            transition: transform 0.25s ease, box-shadow 0.25s ease;
        }

        .job-box:hover {
            transform: translateY(-4px);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 20px rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.08);
            border-top-color: var(--navy-deep);
        }

        .job-box h3 {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: var(--navy-deep);
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .job-box p {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            color: var(--navy-light);
        }

        /* Informational Matrix Cards */
        .overview-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .overview-box {
            background: #fff1f2; /* Soft pink tint for text boxes */
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            border: 1px solid #ffe4e6;
        }

        .overview-box h3 {
            color: var(--pink-deep);
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .overview-box p {
            color: var(--navy-light);
        }

        /* Playful Pop Animation */
        @keyframes popIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: scale(0.97); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
        }

        /* Footer Layout */
        footer {
            background: var(--navy-deep);
            color: #94a3b8;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            margin-top: 60px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            border-top: 4px solid var(--pink-accent);
        }

        /* Flexible Mobile Scaling */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .nav-container {
                flex-direction: column;
                height: auto;
                padding: 12px 0;
                gap: 12px;
            }
            .tab-menu {
                flex-wrap: wrap;
                justify-content: center;
                width: 100%;
            }
            .tab-label {
                font-size: 0.85rem;
                padding: 8px 14px;
            }
            .content-card { padding: 25px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <input type="radio" id="tab1" name="pathway-tabs" class="tab-input" checked>
    <input type="radio" id="tab2" name="pathway-tabs" class="tab-input">
    <input type="radio" id="tab3" name="pathway-tabs" class="tab-input">
    <input type="radio" id="tab4" name="pathway-tabs" class="tab-input">
    <input type="radio" id="tab5" name="pathway-tabs" class="tab-input">

    <nav>
        <div class="nav-container">
            <div class="logo">✨ Biz<span>Pathways</span></div>
            <div class="tab-menu">
                <label for="tab1" class="tab-label label1">Overview</label>
                <label for="tab2" class="tab-label label2">Finance</label>
                <label for="tab3" class="tab-label label3">Marketing</label>
                <label for="tab4" class="tab-label label4">Operations</label>
                <label for="tab5" class="tab-label label5">Consulting & MIS</label>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <header>
        <h1>Business Degree Hub <span>🎀</span></h1>
        <p>Your comprehensive educational guide to exploring specialized fields, operations tracks, and wonderful corporate career pathways.</p>
    </header>

    <div class="container">
        
        <div class="tab-panel" id="content1">
            <div class="content-card">
                <h2>The Power of a Business Degree</h2>
                <p>A business major equips students with fundamental organizational, economic, and behavioral tools that apply to virtually every active global market. Rather than limiting you to one career path, it serves as a multifaceted launchpad.</p>
                
                <div class="overview-grid">
                    <div class="overview-box">
                        <h3>Universal Utility 🌐</h3>
                        <p>Whether your interest lies in healthcare infrastructure, technology startups, or non-profit organizations, clean business administration forms the functional backbone of operations.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="overview-box">
                        <h3>Transferable Skillsets 💫</h3>
                        <p>Develop hard analytical abilities like quantitative risk evaluation alongside softer corporate competencies like collaborative conflict resolution and design thinking.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="overview-box">
                        <h3>Where to Start? 💕</h3>
                        <p>Use the navigation tabs at the top of the webpage to discover specialized industry verticals, entry-level career roles, and core corporate goals.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tab-panel" id="content2">
            <div class="content-card">
                <h2>Finance & Wealth Architecture 📈</h2>
                <p>The study of finance involves tracking liquidity, navigating fluctuating equity markets, evaluating systemic risks, and maximizing organizational value over explicit timeline horizons.</p>
                
                <div class="job-showcase">
                    <div class="job-box">
                        <h3>Financial Analyst</h3>
                        <p>Gathers market indicators, tracks operational expenditure trends, and creates predictive macroeconomic spreadsheets to guide major investment boards.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="job-box">
                        <h3>Investment Banker</h3>
                        <p>Acts as an intermediary agent facilitating massive transactions, raising structural corporate capital, and handling corporate mergers.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="job-box">
                        <h3>Corporate Treasurer</h3>
                        <p>Monitors daily cash inflows and outflows, manages foreign exchange risk, and establishes credit frameworks for business lines.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tab-panel" id="content3">
            <div class="content-card">
                <h2>Marketing & Brand Strategy 🎯</h2>
                <p>Marketing blends analytical consumer insight with expressive design architectures to create, deliver, and communicate tangible product values to target demographics.</p>
                
                <div class="job-showcase">
                    <div class="job-box">
                        <h3>Brand Manager</h3>
                        <p>Acts as the strategic custodian of a product's public perception, ensuring aesthetic uniformity, targeted narrative messaging, and lifecycle execution.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="job-box">
                        <h3>Digital Media Strategist</h3>
                        <p>Maintains conversion frameworks through search algorithms, digital advertising platforms, and comprehensive analytical funnels.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="job-box">
                        <h3>Market Research Analyst</h3>
                        <p>Deploys statistical models, survey methodologies, and competitive analysis matrices to predict whether an emerging market segment is commercially viable.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tab-panel" id="content4">
            <div class="content-card">
                <h2>Operations & Supply Chain Logistics ⚙️</h2>
                <p>Operations personnel analyze resource flows to transform raw materials, software codes, or manual labor into final consumer items with peak structural efficiency.</p>
                
                <div class="job-showcase">
                    <div class="job-box">
                        <h3>Supply Chain Manager</h3>
                        <p>Supervises global vendor relationships, monitors real-time inventory levels, and ensures resilient domestic distribution systems.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="job-box">
                        <h3>Lean Operations Analyst</h3>
                        <p>Audits localized plant assembly patterns or internal office task flows to minimize time delays and structural capital waste.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="job-box">
                        <h3>Procurement Specialist</h3>
                        <p>Negotiates high-volume commercial contracts with manufacturers, confirming material quality standards match regulatory guidelines.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tab-panel" id="content5">
            <div class="content-card">
                <h2>Strategy Consulting & Management Information Systems 💻</h2>
                <p>This hybrid vertical joins structural business consulting logic with modern enterprise software application paths to solve multi-million-dollar tech operational roadblocks.</p>
                
                <div class="job-showcase">
                    <div class="job-box">
                        <h3>Management Consultant</h3>
                        <p>Brought in by exterior companies to diagnose critical profit structural flaws and deliver direct transformation roadmaps.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="job-box">
                        <h3>Technical Product Manager</h3>
                        <p>Coordinates engineering development pipelines, tracking customer feedback metrics to shape cloud-based software feature rollouts.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="job-box">
                        <h3>Business Systems Analyst</h3>
                        <p>Evaluates underlying databases to align enterprise computing resources directly with corporate data workflows.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>

    <footer>
        <p>An educational web resources exploration tool for university business majors.</p>
        <p>Re-stylized with a sophisticated navy and playful pink professional aesthetic color palette.</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
